high_descs: Turn around and face the white table on your right.
Take the silver knife from the table in front of you.
Turn left and face the bin by the table on your right.
Cut the apple inside of the bin in front of you.
Place the knife in the bin in front of you.
Take an apple slice from the can in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave on your left.
Heat the apple in the microwave then take out the apple.
Face the table that the microwave is on.
Place the apple on the table by the microwave in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm apple near the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and make a right to reach the small square white table that is closest.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn left to walk to the trash can.
Slice the apple in the trash can.
Set the knife in the trash can.
Pick up an apple slice from the trash can.
Turn left to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the apple slice in the microwave, removing it again.
Turn to face the table the microwave is sitting on.
Set the apple slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Heat up an apple slice in the microwave to put on a white table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the fridge on the left, then turn right and walk to the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the table.
Turn around, step forward, turn right, go to the end and turn right to face to a trash can with an apple in it.
Slice the apple inside the trash can in thirds..
Slice the right edge of the apple.
Pick up the center piece of the sliced apple.
Turn right, step forward, then turn left and go to the end where there will be a microwave on the left.
Open the microwave, put the apple slice inside and turn on . Wait till it finishes cooking, then remove.
Take a step back from the table.
Place the apple slice on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple in the trash can and cook a piece of it in the microwave.
